description: Deliciously quick and easy cinnamon scrolls.
name: Doughy Cinnamon Scrolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake in oven for 20-30 minutes or until lightly golden. Mix glaze ingredients together to form a thin paste and drizzle over warm scrolls when they come out of the oven.
